================================================================================

ARCHITECTURE
================================================================================

This extension uses a sidecar architecture with two main components:

- Frontend: TypeScript-based VS Code extension
- Backend: C# console application using Roslyn for semantic analysis

Communication between components uses a custom length-prefixed protocol over
stdin/stdout.

